
The following flags may be set or cleared:
	SET <flag>		 CLEAR <flag>

auto        Enable auto attack.
echo        Communications echo enabled.
home        Makes the current room a 'teleport home' room.
ignore      Ignore all communications from other players.
nobroad     Disable all broadcast messages sent to you.
nologin     Disable all login messages sent to you.
nosummon    Disables ability of others to cast summon on your character.
nocop       Others cannot copulate with you.
prompt      Enables the display of HP & MP with the prompt.
split       You will auto-split any gold with your group followers.
nofollow    Others cannot follow you.
wimpy       Your character will automatically flee when HP is low.
            (You can also set the HP level:  set wimpy <value>)
